<h2>signal</h2>
    <p>This attribute can only be used to modify class and category. Class object generated by the current class can use signal mechanism. For example: </p>
    <pre class="code">
component Demo
{
    бнбн
    [uuid(cec0fb61-756d-4d5b-a959-8ff369072c61), <b>signal</b>]
    class CDemo {
        бнбн
    }
}
</pre>
    <p></p>
    <p>If the component uses this attribute, then the client program can invoke <a class="style1" href="../inline_func/MyCSignalPart.htm">MyCSignalPart</a> method to obtain class smart pointer <a class="style1" href="../../../zee/class/CSignalRef.htm">CSignalRef</a>.All methods in class <a class="style1" href="../../../zee/class/CSignal.htm">CSignal</a> can be used.</p>
    <p>This attribute can be used with other attributes.</p>
